{
    "content": "<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\"><strong>这里普及一下，宝珠通过附魔增加技能具体参数提升的写法，</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\"><strong>也就是市面上所谓的侍魂宝珠。</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">先说一下宝珠的构成。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\"><strong>普通宝珠的构成：宝珠文件、卡片文件</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\"><strong>技能宝珠的构成：宝珠文件、卡片文件、卡片调用的APD文件</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">所以说，很简单，在对道具的基础写法完全掌握了的情况下，写一个APD调用就可以了。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\"><strong>下面是卡片调用APD的代码写法：</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[enchant]</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[if]</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[change status]<br />\n`hp`<br />\n`&gt;`<br />\n`%`<br />\n0&nbsp;`end`</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[/if]</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[then]</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[target]<br />\n`myself`<br />\n-1&nbsp;<br />\n[appendage]<br />\n这里写APD编号，例如51&nbsp;<br />\n[/then]</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[/enchant]</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\"><strong>也就是卡片使用IF代码，触发APD附加状态。</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\"><strong>下面是APD的组成：</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">#PVF_File</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[type]<br />\n&nbsp;`skill data up`</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[duration]<br />\n&nbsp;20000</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[buff]<br />\n&nbsp;0</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[icon image]<br />\n&nbsp;``&nbsp;0</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[max overlap]<br />\n&nbsp;1</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[int data]<br />\n[/int data]</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[string data]<br />\n这里写技能提升参数<br />\n就写在这个位置<br />\n不会写技能提升参数<br />\n就自己去学<br />\n参考本百科里部分资料<br />\n或其他类型教程<br />\n或者自己去找个异界装备<br />\n参考一下技能参数提升怎么写！<br />\n[/string data]</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[float data]<br />\n[/float data]</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\"><strong>把以上代码写成apd，就可以了，不要忘了新增APD列表，并查代码重复</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\"><strong>注意：</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[max overlap]<br />\n&nbsp;1</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\"><strong>这个代表APD附加状态的最大叠加次数！</strong></span></p>",
